nodes.title: Notes on using the workflow
widgets_values:
In this workflow, the groups are bypassed by default. 
You can right-click on the groups to change this.
You can use this for groups and also for individual notes.

For example, saving in the individual groups can be switched off
(right-click and select Bypass).

The additional tool groups can be switched on and off. 
Please note that switching off is only possible for tools at the end of a workflow.
Use bypass within a workflow.

All tool groups, Loras, Controlnet, IP adapters are set to Bypass.
Set Group Nodes to Always to switch them on!
Set Bypass Group Nodes to switch them off.

With the Phytongosssss Loader you can use thumbnails for model selection, 
works with the Lora loaders.


If you set Global Seed to fixed and start it, you can gradually start Additional Tools and Face Optimization, then everything that has already been calculated will not be recalculated.


I'm happy about a response

Have fun, Murphylanga

nodes.title: rebuilding the connections of the noodles
widgets_values:
If you reconnect the noddles. 

If you use bypass, you can simply switch the Ucpscale and Highresfix groups on and off, regardless of where they are connected.

But this does not work for face optimization and swapping faces.

For face optimization, you can choose the order in which you want to work.

I often use the following order to make an initial selection:
Standard - Select Start - Finish.

For high quality images with faces:
Start - to highresfix - from highresfix - to detailer 1 - from detailer 1 - to upscale step 1 - from upscale 1 step - to image sharpen - to detailer 2 - from detailer 2 - to face crop - from face crop - to upscale step 2 - from upscale step 2 - to exit (or face swap).

Other connections are also possible as long as you do not insert a loop. Try it out and explore the possibilities. 
 

The Highresfix and Upscale groups are always easy to add or switch on and switch off with a bypass.

If you don't change any inputs and have the global seed set to fixed, only what has not yet been calculated will be calculated.

The facecrop group had an error from time to time. That's why an additional toggle of VEA encode and VEA decode is used.

Have fun, Murphylanga
